nl.bioinf.lscheffer_wvanhelvoirt.insanemodel.model

Class Solvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.bioinf.lscheffer_wvanhelvoirt.insanemodel.model.Solvent

  • public class Solvent
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents all selected solvents that will be used in insane.py. This class contains an array of all used valid solvent types, and other solvent related parameters.
